title: Yuki Okaniwa
text:
is a Japanese <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="Tochigi%20City%20FC">Tochigi City FC</a>.
Career.
Yuki Okaniwa joined <a href="J2%20League">J2 League</a> club <a href="Thespakusatsu%20Gunma">Thespakusatsu Gunma</a> in 2017.
Club statistics.
"Updated to 22 February 2020".
